page.title: 06FAMILY LIFE
page.content: When I arrived at school we did a tables test. I got 19 out of 24 so I had to stay in and learn them. Then we went swimming. I did my 200 metres then we went back to school and we did art. Then Mrs Purdam had us for songs and story.It got to 3.30 and we had to go home . When I got home I put my roller-skates on.Then we had tea. It was mince with Yorshire pudding. Then I went back out side again.Then I came in and my dad wanted me to take the dog a walk. So I took him.When I got back home I sat on my bean bag while my dad was trying to sell a gas fire and at 9.00 clock I went to bed.
